    "synopsis": "The world of Herodian IV is doomed: the great Hive Fleets of the Tyranids have descended from the void, intent on devouring everything that lives. In the hours before the planet falls, Inquisitor Kalypsia and a kill-team of Deathwatch Space Marines, veterans drawn from many Chapters, are dispatched to a remote research outpost to recover a vital secret. But they have been betrayed, and the truth they uncover may be a fate worse than the swarm itself. Hunted by ravenous alien hordes and a traitor hidden among the Imperium's own, Kalypsia and her warriors must escape a dying world before it is stripped to the bone.",
